[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6560,
        "end_time": 8681,
        "text": "Way before the first selfie,"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 8681,
        "end_time": 10883,
        "text": "the ancient Greeks and Romans had a myth"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 10883,
        "end_time": 14605,
        "text": "about someone a little too obsessed \nwith his own image."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 14605,
        "end_time": 15895,
        "text": "In one telling,"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 15895,
        "end_time": 20779,
        "text": "Narcissus was a handsome guy wandering\nthe world in search of someone to love."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 20779,
        "end_time": 23235,
        "text": "After rejecting a nymph named Echo,"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 23235,
        "end_time": 26709,
        "text": "he caught a glimpse \nof his own reflection in a river,"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 26709,
        "end_time": 28511,
        "text": "and fell in love with it."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 28511,
        "end_time": 30116,
        "text": "Unable to tear himself away,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 30116,
        "end_time": 31944,
        "text": "Narcissus drowned."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 31944,
        "end_time": 37040,
        "text": "A flower marked the spot of where he died,\nand we call that flower the Narcissus."
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 37040,
        "end_time": 40391,
        "text": "The myth captures \nthe basic idea of narcissism,"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 40391,
        "end_time": 44180,
        "text": "elevated and sometimes \ndetrimental self-involvement."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 44180,
        "end_time": 48274,
        "text": "But it&#39;s not just a personality type\nthat shows up in advice columns."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 48274,
        "end_time": 52966,
        "text": "It&#39;s actually a set of traits classified\nand studied by psychologists."
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 52966,
        "end_time": 58772,
        "text": "The psychological definition of narcissism\nis an inflated, grandiose self-image."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 58772,
        "end_time": 62119,
        "text": "To varying degrees, narcissists think\nthey&#39;re better looking,"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 62119,
        "end_time": 62973,
        "text": "smarter,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 62973,
        "end_time": 65233,
        "text": "and more important than other people,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 65233,
        "end_time": 68011,
        "text": "and that they deserve special treatment."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 68011,
        "end_time": 72767,
        "text": "Psychologists recognize two forms\nof narcissism as a personality trait:"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 72767,
        "end_time": 75889,
        "text": "grandiose and vulnerable narcissism."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 75889,
        "end_time": 78406,
        "text": "There&#39;s also narcissistic \npersonality disorder,"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 78406,
        "end_time": 82066,
        "text": "a more extreme form,\nwhich we&#39;ll return to shortly."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 82066,
        "end_time": 85801,
        "text": "Grandiose narcissism \nis the most familiar kind,"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 85801,
        "end_time": 87789,
        "text": "characterized by extroversion,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 87789,
        "end_time": 88956,
        "text": "dominance,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 88956,
        "end_time": 90531,
        "text": "and attention seeking."
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 90531,
        "end_time": 93812,
        "text": "Grandiose narcissists pursue \nattention and power,"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 93812,
        "end_time": 95457,
        "text": "sometimes as politicians,"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 95457,
        "end_time": 96457,
        "text": "celebrities,"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 96457,
        "end_time": 98290,
        "text": "or cultural leaders."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 98290,
        "end_time": 102636,
        "text": "Of course, not everyone who pursues\nthese positions of power is narcissistic."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 102636,
        "end_time": 104406,
        "text": "Many do it for very positive reasons,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 104406,
        "end_time": 106082,
        "text": "like reaching their full potential,"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 106082,
        "end_time": 108491,
        "text": "or helping make people&#39;s lives better."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 108491,
        "end_time": 110777,
        "text": "But narcissistic individuals seek power"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 110777,
        "end_time": 113773,
        "text": "for the status \nand attention that goes with it."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 113773,
        "end_time": 117919,
        "text": "Meanwhile, vulnerable narcissists\ncan be quiet and reserved."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 117919,
        "end_time": 119833,
        "text": "They have a strong sense of entitlement,"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 119833,
        "end_time": 122793,
        "text": "but are easily threatened or slighted."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 122793,
        "end_time": 127061,
        "text": "In either case, the dark side of\nnarcissism shows up over the long term."
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 127061,
        "end_time": 129991,
        "text": "Narcissists tend to act selfishly,"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 129991,
        "end_time": 134376,
        "text": "so narcissistic leaders may make risky\nor unethical decisions,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 134376,
        "end_time": 139144,
        "text": "and narcissistic partners may be dishonest\nor unfaithful."
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 139144,
        "end_time": 141680,
        "text": "When their rosy view of themselves\nis challenged,"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 141680,
        "end_time": 144223,
        "text": "they can become resentful and aggressive."
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 144223,
        "end_time": 147184,
        "text": "It&#39;s like a disease where the sufferers\nfeel pretty good,"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 147184,
        "end_time": 149505,
        "text": "but the people around them suffer."
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 149505,
        "end_time": 150918,
        "text": "Taken to the extreme,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 150918,
        "end_time": 154208,
        "text": "this behavior is classified \nas a psychological disorder"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 154208,
        "end_time": 156964,
        "text": "called narcissistic personality disorder."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 156964,
        "end_time": 159927,
        "text": "It affects one to two percent\nof the population,"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 159927,
        "end_time": 161506,
        "text": "more commonly men."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 161506,
        "end_time": 164664,
        "text": "It is also a diagnosis \nreserved for adults."
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 164664,
        "end_time": 168145,
        "text": "Young people, especially children,\ncan be very self-centered,"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 168145,
        "end_time": 171491,
        "text": "but this might just be a normal\npart of development."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 171491,
        "end_time": 174772,
        "text": "The fifth edition of the American\nPsychiatric Association&#39;s"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 174772,
        "end_time": 177311,
        "text": "Diagnostic and Statistical Manual"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 177311,
        "end_time": 181858,
        "text": "describes several traits associated\nwith narcissistic personality disorder."
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 181858,
        "end_time": 184778,
        "text": "They include a grandiose view of oneself,"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 184778,
        "end_time": 186157,
        "text": "problems with empathy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 186157,
        "end_time": 187773,
        "text": "a sense of entitlement,"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 187773,
        "end_time": 190804,
        "text": "and a need for admiration or attention."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 190804,
        "end_time": 193542,
        "text": "What makes these trait a true\npersonality disorder"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 193542,
        "end_time": 197889,
        "text": "is that they take over people&#39;s lives\nand cause significant problems."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 197889,
        "end_time": 201097,
        "text": "Imagine that instead of caring\nfor your spouse or children,"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 201097,
        "end_time": 204429,
        "text": "you used them as a source\nof attention or admiration."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 204429,
        "end_time": 206102,
        "text": "Or imagine that instead of seeking"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 206102,
        "end_time": 208408,
        "text": "constructive feedback \nabout your performance,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 208408,
        "end_time": 210797,
        "text": "you instead told everyone \nwho tried to help you"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 210797,
        "end_time": 212908,
        "text": "that they were wrong."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 212908,
        "end_time": 215230,
        "text": "So what causes narcissism?"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 215230,
        "end_time": 217969,
        "text": "Twin studies show \na strong genetic component,"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 217969,
        "end_time": 221023,
        "text": "although we don&#39;t know \nwhich genes are involved."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 221023,
        "end_time": 222895,
        "text": "But environment matters, too."
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 222895,
        "end_time": 225240,
        "text": "Parents who put their child\non a pedestal"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 225240,
        "end_time": 227789,
        "text": "can foster grandiose narcissism."
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 227789,
        "end_time": 233050,
        "text": "And cold, controlling parents\ncan contribute to vulnerable narcissism."
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 233050,
        "end_time": 235259,
        "text": "Narcissism also seems to be higher"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 235259,
        "end_time": 239429,
        "text": "in cultures that value individuality\nand self-promotion."
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 239429,
        "end_time": 241170,
        "text": "In the United States, for example,"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 241170,
        "end_time": 245902,
        "text": "narcissism as a personality trait\nhas been rising since the 1970s,"
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 245902,
        "end_time": 247991,
        "text": "when the communal focus of the 60s"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 247991,
        "end_time": 250150,
        "text": "gave way to the self-esteem movement"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 250150,
        "end_time": 252633,
        "text": "and a rise in materialism."
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 252633,
        "end_time": 257078,
        "text": "More recently, social media has multiplied\nthe possibilities for self-promotion,"
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 257078,
        "end_time": 258371,
        "text": "though it&#39;s worth noting"
    },
    {
        "index": 89,
        "start_time": 258371,
        "end_time": 262191,
        "text": "that there&#39;s no clear evidence\nthat social media causes narcissism."
    },
    {
        "index": 90,
        "start_time": 262191,
        "end_time": 267764,
        "text": "Rather, it provides narcissists a means\nto seek social status and attention."
    },
    {
        "index": 91,
        "start_time": 267764,
        "end_time": 271235,
        "text": "So can narcissists improve \non those negative traits?"
    },
    {
        "index": 92,
        "start_time": 271235,
        "end_time": 272474,
        "text": "Yes!"
    },
    {
        "index": 93,
        "start_time": 272474,
        "end_time": 275450,
        "text": "Anything that promotes honest reflection\non their own behavior"
    },
    {
        "index": 94,
        "start_time": 275450,
        "end_time": 277104,
        "text": "and caring for others,"
    },
    {
        "index": 95,
        "start_time": 277104,
        "end_time": 282116,
        "text": "like psychotherapy or practicing \ncompassion towards others, can be helpful."
    },
    {
        "index": 96,
        "start_time": 282116,
        "end_time": 284172,
        "text": "The difficulty is it can be challenging"
    },
    {
        "index": 97,
        "start_time": 284172,
        "end_time": 286712,
        "text": "for people with \nnarcissistic personality disorder"
    },
    {
        "index": 98,
        "start_time": 286712,
        "end_time": 288911,
        "text": "to keep working at self-betterment."
    },
    {
        "index": 99,
        "start_time": 288911,
        "end_time": 293763,
        "text": "For a narcissist, self-reflection is hard\nfrom an unflattering angle."
    }
]